{"word":"H1254 - בָּרָא - bârâʼ - baw-raw' - Choose","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּרָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bârâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Choose"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிருஷ்டி, உண்டாக்கு, படை, நேரிடச்செய், வெட்டிப்போடு, தெரிந்துகொள், கொழுக்கப்பண்ணு. சிருஷ்டிக்கப்படு, உண்டாக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to create, to shape, to form"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to shape, to fashion, to create (always with God as subject)"},{"paragraph":"1) used of heaven and earth"},{"paragraph":"2) used of individual man"},{"paragraph":"3) used of new conditions and circumstances"},{"paragraph":"4) used of transformations"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be created"},{"paragraph":"1) used of heaven and earth"},{"paragraph":"2) used of birth"},{"paragraph":"3) used of something new"},{"paragraph":"4) used of miracles"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cut down"},{"paragraph":"2) to cut out"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"2) to be fat; (Hiphil) to make yourselves fat"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; (absolutely) to <i>create</i>; (qualified) to <i>cut</i> down (a wood), <i>select</i>, <i>feed</i> (as formative processes): - choose, create (creator), cut down, dispatch, do, make (fat)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1254 - בָּרָא - bârâʼ - baw-raw'/1254\">H1254</a>, <a href=\"#/H1256 - בְּרָאיָה - Bᵉrâʼyâh - ber-aw-yaw'/1256\">H1256</a>, <a href=\"#/H1274 - בְּרִי - bᵉrîy - ber-ee'/1274\">H1274</a>, <a href=\"#/H1277 - בָּרִיא - bârîyʼ - baw-ree'/1277\">H1277</a>, <a href=\"#/H1278 - בְּרִיאָה - bᵉrîyʼâh - ber-ee-aw'/1278\">H1278</a>"}]}